      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm finally parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car has been my baby\u2014always garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. You won't find a single blemish on it! It drives perfectly and smells like new. If you're looking for a ride that's in truly flawless condition, you've found it! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
