    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is a museum-quality E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system. This example is mechanically flawless, with preventative maintenance performed on the rod bearings and the rear subframe reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power to the rear wheels through a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. Every bushing, seal, and suspension component remains in factory-spec condition, offering the precise turn-in and communicative chassis feedback these cars are legendary for. Documented service history included.",
      "price": 48500.0,
