    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true 'time-capsule' specimen that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional ceramic coating; there are absolutely no stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Every panel gap is factory-perfect, and the alloy wheels are free of even the slightest curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition, retaining that original factory scent. The premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the carpets are pristine under protective mats, and every electronic feature\u2014from the navigation to the ambient lighting\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a complete service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule. The engine bay is detailed and dry, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle in peak aesthetic and mechanical health.",
